15 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
16 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 4 O.S. 2021, Section 30.8, is
17 amended to read as follows:
18 Section 30.8. A. An animal shelter operator or commercial pet
19 breeder who is not in violation of the Commercial Pet Breeders and
20 Animal Shelter Licensing Act or any rule adopted under the
21 Commercial Pet Breeders and Animal Shelter Licensing Act may renew
22 the license of the person by:
23
